          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3982049-amy-sturgis?shelf=20th-century">20th-century</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3982049-amy-sturgis?shelf=sf-in-translation">sf-in-translation</a>, 
